# RES Phase 1 — Build Walkthrough

## What Was Built

Phase 1 delivers the complete foundation of the Repair Execution System.

---

## Project Structure Created

```
RES/
├── main.py              ← App entry point (Qt bootstrap, theme, i18n)
├── config.py            ← All settings from .env (single source of truth)
├── .env                 ← Secrets & DB URL (never commit to git)
├── .gitignore
│
├── core/
│   ├── database.py      ← SQLAlchemy engine + session factory (SQLite/PostgreSQL)
│   ├── models.py        ← All 12 ORM tables
│   ├── seeds.py         ← Default pipeline + admin user seeding
│   ├── process_engine.py← Check-in/out, routing, capacity, transit time
│   ├── capacity_tracker.py ← Bay occupancy, capacity-block vs staff-delay
│   └── time_tracker.py  ← Elapsed, remaining, transit, variance, color-coding
│
├── services/
│   ├── auth_service.py  ← bcrypt login, roles, session
│   └── notification_service.py ← Client WhatsApp/SMS dispatcher
│
├── ui/
│   ├── main_window.py   ← Shell: sidebar nav + role gating
│   ├── login_screen.py  ← Login card with error handling
│   ├── dashboard_widget.py ← Kanban board with auto-refresh
│   └── vehicle_card_widget.py ← Vehicle card with color-coded timers
│
├── assets/
│   └── styles/theme.qss ← Full dark industrial Qt stylesheet
│
├── cost_estimator/      ← Subproject placeholder (Phase 7)
└── tests/               ← Test package (Phase 8)
```

---

## Database Verification

All 12 tables created and 8 repair pipeline processes seeded:

| Seq | Process | Capacity | Severity |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Vehicle Reception | 1 | All |
| 2 | Mechanic Work | 2 | HIGH only |
| 3 | Straightening | 2 | All |
| 4 | Preparation to Paint | 2 | All |
| 5 | Painting | 1 | All |
| 6 | Assembly | 2 | All |
| 7 | Polishing | 2 | All |
| 8 | Quality Assurance | 1 | All |

Default admin user created: `admin / admin1234` *(change immediately after first login)*

---

## Key Design Decisions Implemented

- **SQLAlchemy ORM** — switch to PostgreSQL by changing one [.env](file:///c:/Users/mxgs2/Workspaces/VSCode_Antigravity/Python/RES/.env) line
- **Soft deletes** on Vehicle — nothing is ever permanently removed
- **`cost_estimator_ref` hook** on Finding — ready for Phase 7 AI integration
- **`max_capacity`** on Process — powers bay occupancy and delay-reason tracking
- **`insurance_acknowledged_at`** on Finding — SLA KPI for insurance response time
- **All user-facing strings** use `self.tr()` — i18n ready from day one
- **Dark theme** with color-coded vehicle cards (green/amber/red)
- **Role-based navigation** — insurance-viewer sees only Insurance Dashboard

---

## How to Run

```powershell
# Activate venv and launch
.\venv_Qt\Scripts\python.exe main.py

# Or reset and re-seed the database
.\venv_Qt\Scripts\python.exe -c "from core.database import init_db; from core.seeds import seed_all; init_db(); seed_all()"
```

**Login:** [admin](file:///c:/Users/mxgs2/Workspaces/VSCode_Antigravity/Python/RES/core/seeds.py#64-87) / `admin1234`

